This is a class to create a socket-based server easily in PHP


FILES

example.php     : just an exemple file

ClsSocketServer : the class to extend to create your socket server


REQUIREMENTS

- PHP 5 or later
- PHP socket functions (most of the distribs have them by default)


INSTALLATION

1. Read www.cyrilmazur.com to find out more

2. You can add a daemon behavior to your socket server with another tutorial on www.cyrilmazur.com


More info at www.cyrilmazur.com

Enjoy ;-)

